<p><span class="userblue">~dirmoose:</span> Nope</p>
<p><span class="userblue">~dirmoose:</span> <span class="usergray">jrdeneal</span> What do we have?</p>
<p><span class="usergray">&amp;jrdeneal:</span> My guys are taking inventory rn</p>
<p><span class="usergray">&amp;jrdeneal:</span> No real conclusion yet, but we can speculate</p>
